---
title: Honey Mustard Double Sausage Traybake with Buttery Onion Sauce
description: In this traybake, we're roasting potatoes, carrots, onion, sausages and apples on trays in the oven, giving you time to make an easy but delicious buttery sauce to spoon over the top once it's all ready.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R03_W38_UK_R2150-70_MAin_F1_low_2-e9bc3ecf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/6698e87b9b6afed05f640df1-en-GB.pdf
